headline: AstraZeneca ups investment in Virginia; Moderna vets launch VC fund
summary: The British pharma is adding $500 million, and ADC production capabilities, to a planned Virginia facility. Elsewhere, Ferring announced layoffs and Sanofi touted a radiopharmaceutical drug.
